Court officers require that criminal proceedings be immediately suspended.
The majority of the occupants did not participate in the degradations.
Legitimation of protests
The young people of the Verdi trade union in the service sector and the German Confederation of Trade Unions (DGB) show solidarity with the students.
Protests are only a legitimate expression of growing concern for our own future, says Alexander Klein, Verdi Union's Regional Youth Secretary.
As for the Minister of Science of the Land of Hesse Eva Kühne-Hörmann (CDU), she took the case for the action taken by the President of the University and the police.
We thank the President of the University.
